pidgin-whatsapp (0.4-2) quantal; urgency=low

  * Many bugfixes
    - Fix for image upload (whenever we upload an image twice)
    - Fix ping parsing, avoids disconnects
    - Fixed a memory leak, this should alleviate memory consumption
  * Some other bugs not affecting Unix-like platforms

 -- David Guillen Fandos <david@davidgf.net>  Mon, 2 Feb 2014 23:40:00 +0200

pidgin-whatsapp (0.4-1) quantal; urgency=low

  * Updated WhatsApp API to the newest version (v1.4)
    - Contact statuses working again
    - Sending images might not work, please check
    - No more update messages from WA server
  * Other small bugs such as profile photo querying...

 -- David Guillen Fandos <david@davidgf.net>  Mon, 28 Jan 2014 00:15:00 +0200

